title: Parmesan breadsticks
ingredients: ['425g (15oz) white bread flour', '100g (3½oz) Parmesan cheese, freshly grated', '2 tsp chopped fresh rosemary or ½ tsp dried rosemary', '1 tsp pepper', '1 tsp easy-blend dried yeast', '300ml (10fl oz) lukewarm water', '4 tbsp semolina or polenta', '1 tsp olive oil']
